{
  "stem": "1400.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But to be in a camp, in the bunk beds, three high, eight, 10 of us on one level, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we shared blankets, one underneath us, one above us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The dehumanizing condition that we went through, you didn't count.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't-- didn't-- it was-- it was so that-- that you were ordered every morning, sun or rain or cold, snow, outside for a count.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They called it appel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we had to line up and stand there and wait for the commandant to come around and take count.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in the wintertime, we huddled together against the back of the barrack to keep warm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were changing-- the last man went front, to-- because of the middle man was the warmest position.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we were changing for hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was going on, sometimes from 6 o'clock in the morning till 9:00.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when it came to feeding time-- I have to say feeding time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was such that the first man got a bucket in his hand, a-- a pan.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They measured in five, eight ladles of soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They counted down five or eight people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we sit around this pot, a spoon at a time, went around till it was gone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because I wasn't in Auschwitz more than a week, I realized food meant life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You have to get your share.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we watched each other, that everybody gets no more than their share.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Everybody was going to different for details.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I went front of Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Mengele again, and again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I wasn't selected into that transport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I stayed in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And at one time, they asked people to work-- for work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I put up my hand, and I got a job on the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
